    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的收入比预期的少了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/blackrock-blk-misses-long-term-flow-expectations-amid-asia-outflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司（Blackrock Inc.）在总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的全面关税上发布了本季度的不同结果，收取的客户资金少于分析师的预期，但每股收益高于预期的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/blackrock-blk-misses-long-term-flow-expectations-amid-asia-outflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 10:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库突然在警告特朗普的警告时突然交易像风险的资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的岩石固定安全性，美国国债债券在恐慌时期一直是投资者的首个征集港口。他们在9/11的全球金融危机期间集会，即使在美国自己的信用等级也被削减时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
